settings page.
<% end %></p>
</div>

<div class="qa">
<h2>Where is my API token?</h2>
<p>You can find your API token on your <a href="https://pinboard.in/settings/">
    Pinboard settings</a> page.</p>
</div>

<div class="qa">
<h2>Are all my shared items and comments public?</h2>
<p>Yes, for now. Groups are one of many features I hope to
include eventually.</p>
</div>

<div class="qa">
<h2>Do I have to use my real name?</h2>
<p>No, but you do have to use <em>a</em> name.</p>
</div>

<div class="qa">
<h2>Is all my Pushpin data safe forever?</h2>
<p>Absolutely not. This is a very early prototype and anything 
   may break at any time.</p>
</div>


